					"type": 23,
					"value": "Aradin is yelling to Klank because it is blocking the entrance to the Sorcerous Sundries shop. Aradin asks the player whether they had success on the quest of the nightsong and leaves.\r\n\r\nLORR-oh-AH-kan."
